"\"<p data-start=\\\"225\\\" data-end=\\\"490\\\">In today\u2019s fast-paced workplace, leaders often face the challenge of driving results while maintaining a healthy team environment. <em data-start=\\\"356\\\" data-end=\\\"386\\\">Compassionate Accountability<\/em> equips leaders with the skills to manage performance effectively <strong data-start=\\\"452\\\" data-end=\\\"487\\\">without creating stress or fear<\/strong>.<\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"492\\\" data-end=\\\"541\\\">In this interactive session, participants will:<br><br><\/p>\\n<ul data-start=\\\"542\\\" data-end=\\\"793\\\">\\n<li data-start=\\\"542\\\" data-end=\\\"617\\\">\\n<p data-start=\\\"544\\\" data-end=\\\"617\\\">Learn to <strong data-start=\\\"553\\\" data-end=\\\"614\\\">differentiate between healthy pressure and harmful stress<\/strong>.<\/p>\\n<\/li>\\n<li data-start=\\\"618\\\" data-end=\\\"707\\\">\\n<p data-start=\\\"620\\\" data-end=\\\"707\\\">Master <strong data-start=\\\"627\\\" data-end=\\\"654\\\">difficult conversations<\/strong>, giving feedback without triggering defensiveness.<\/p>\\n<\/li>\\n<li data-start=\\\"708\\\" data-end=\\\"793\\\">\\n<p data-start=\\\"710\\\" data-end=\\\"793\\\">Recognize <strong data-start=\\\"720\\\" data-end=\\\"775\\\">early warning signs of burnout and vicarious trauma<\/strong> in their teams.<\/p>\\n<\/li><li data-start=\\\"708\\\" data-end=\\\"793\\\"><p data-start=\\\"710\\\" data-end=\\\"793\\\"><br><\/p><\/li>\\n<\/ul>\\n<p data-start=\\\"795\\\" data-end=\\\"997\\\">Through practical strategies, real-life scenarios, and reflective exercises, this workshop helps leaders <strong data-start=\\\"900\\\" data-end=\\\"994\\\">create a culture of accountability that motivates, supports, and sustains high performance<\/strong>.<\/p>\""